org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN issue_statuses ON issue_statuses.id = issues.status_id INNER JOIN trackers ON trackers.id = issues.tracker_id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN enumerations ON enumerations.id = issues.priority_id AND enumerations.type IN ('IssuePriority') WHERE issues.id IN (SELECT customized_id FROM custom_values WHERE customized_type = 'Issue' AND custom_field_id = 22 AND CAST(CASE WHEN value = '' THEN '0' ELSE value END AS DECIMAL(30, 0)) IN (SELECT customized_id FROM custom_values WHERE customized_type = 'Version' AND custom_field_id = 23 AND custom_values.value IN ('ABC')))
